{
  "stem": "311.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The horses I see at the race track, they don't have anything on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the weight means a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're-- they're-- they're-- they're just as beautiful, and maybe more beautiful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'm sure they're more expensive, and they don't have any jewelry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, every Polack wanted to arrive or to dress up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he was going to church and he was-- and then, the taxis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the-- how would you call the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, it wouldn't be balagula.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But if you want to go to the train, there were no taxis in-- in 1930s, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were stand up, one-- I tell you, across the street where we were living, they were standing in line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you wanted to go to, you know, to the railroad, or you want to go bring something to somebody, or you visit some guests, you took those buggies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you didn't take them, you hire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in line, you had to take the first one, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had like a union between themselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those horses, everybody tried to dress up and polish his buggy as nice as he could, and see that every couple years he puts a coat of paint on it, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was an item.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was an item that families-- we made a beautiful living out of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, in about 1935, '36, my father started-- came out with an idea we're going to do some sport items.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we started with ski poles, you know, bamboo, and the other kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we used to put the-- the handles on it, and the wheels, and the points, and the-- you know, and we sold it.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
